# This repo tracks the code files plus the image assets the talisman board
# uses (reference/{talismans,details,backgrounds}). The CAIN rulebook
# PDFs/plaintext, the generated notes, and the rest of the reference material
# are deliberately left untracked (large, mostly third-party material).
# Whitelist approach: ignore everything, then re-include what we keep.

# Ignore everything at the root by default...
/*

# ...but keep the code files, the docs, and this ignore list.
!.gitignore
!talismans.html
!open-talismans.command
!open-talismans.bat
!README.md
!LICENSE
!demo.gif

# ...and the image folders the board draws from. A parent dir must be
# un-ignored before anything inside it can be, hence the two-step.
!/reference/
/reference/*
!/reference/talismans/
!/reference/details/
!/reference/backgrounds/

.DS_Store
